        {
            "title": "特斯拉據悉正研發支持蘋果CarPlay的功能 馬斯克多年抵觸後或讓步",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"Tesla Model 3 vehicles at the company’s store in Vallejo, California.\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/niINJWejSijEb8ZaX03dPA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/b81a55fa930e1e2b006d931ec71abd4d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Tesla Model 3 vehicles at the company’s store in Vallejo, California.</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 知情人士表示，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:特斯拉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特斯拉\">特斯拉</a>正在開發支持蘋果公司CarPlay系統的功能。這是客戶長期以來呼聲最高的功能之一。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據知情人士透露，特斯拉已開始內測這項功能。由於該項目仍處於未公開階段，知情人士要求匿名。其他汽車製造商長期以來一直支持CarPlay平台 —— 該平台可顯示為車載信息娛樂系統優化的iPhone軟件版本，被許多用戶看作「必備配置」。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">增加CarPlay標志著特斯拉及其執行長馬斯克的驚人轉變。馬斯克長期以來一直無視用戶添加這項熱門功能的請求。他多年來一直批評蘋果公司，尤其不滿其應用商店政策。此外，蘋果啟動造車計畫時從特斯拉挖走了工程師，也引起了馬斯克的不滿。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9ebb0713-0645-3db1-a4c7-e9568993d1b8-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"位於加利福尼亞州瓦列霍市特斯拉門店的特斯拉Model 3車型攝影：DavidPaulMorris/彭博\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/VeG.ssvO4cRKnaFeS9bp8A--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/255ec6c94a47c8f059f6272e07563950\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">位於加利福尼亞州瓦列霍市特斯拉門店的特斯拉Model 3車型攝影：DavidPaulMorris/彭博</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，特斯拉已討論在未來幾個月內推出支持CarPlay的功能，但計畫尚未最終敲定，發布時間可能會有所延遲。此外，該公司也曾多次在研發數月甚至數年後取消或推遲發布新功能。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">特斯拉未回應置評請求。蘋果公司代表拒絕置評。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Tesla Developing Apple CarPlay Support in Bid to Boost Car Sales</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E6%AD%A3%E7%A0%94%E7%99%BC%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9Ccarplay%E7%9A%84%E5%8A%9F%E8%83%BD-%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E5%A4%9A%E5%B9%B4%E6%8A%B5%E8%A7%B8%E5%BE%8C%E6%88%96%E8%AE%93%E6%AD%A5-173856740.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-14 02:10:45",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
