        {
            "title": "國際能源署連續第六個月上調全球石油供應過剩量預測",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"567\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Oip9kGxjviGAheUbkcqZww--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2NztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e054e1c75a4edd1d7e7bf14b12946b8d\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 在OPEC+持續恢復供應、需求成長依然疲軟之際，國際能源署(<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:IEA;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/IEA\">IEA</a>)連續第六個月上調對明年全球石油過剩量的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">報告稱，2026年全球石油日供應量將比需求多出約400萬桶，較上月預測略有增加。IEA指出，全球石油「供需平衡日益失衡」，該機構自6月以來每月都上調過剩量預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">IEA石油市場與行業部門負責人Toril Bosoni在接受彭博電視採訪時表示：「我們看到全球原油供應仍在持續增加，而需求成長相對溫和。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-1bb8b6c7-01e9-3e08-8bf9-94ce55227033-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/KCJZD99JPm83NS5sg3w6eA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/503152244a0ee52ed3c3d0d41ae9197d\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本月早些時候，OPEC及其盟友同意12月再次小幅增產，並在明年第一季度暫停進一步增產。IEA數據顯示，明年新增供應量中至少有一半來自OPEC+國家。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Bosoni補充說，美國對俄羅斯石油生產商實施的新制裁影響仍不確定，但對供應構成「重大風險」。華盛頓已針對俄羅斯兩大石油公司Rosneft和盧克石油採取措施，以施壓普丁結束對烏克蘭的戰爭。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">IEA略微上調了今年和明年的全球石油需求成長預期，但仍預計日均成長不足80萬桶，顯著低於近幾十年的平均水平。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"567\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jwVN50_Y_bP13WsoQBrMng--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU2NztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/2bab86f1f2110b598b1dc08e79b6a2ae\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">IEA的短期報告顯示，隨著電動汽車的普及加速，全球石油需求將在本十年末停止成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">IEA指出，短期內供過於求的跡象已現。全球觀測到的石油庫存9月攀升至四年來新高，對油價形成壓力。周三倫敦市場原油價格下跌3.8%，至每桶63美元以下。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題IEA Boosts Forecast of Record Oil Glut for a Sixth Month (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Lizzy Burden.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%83%BD%E6%BA%90%E7%BD%B2%E9%80%A3%E7%BA%8C%E7%AC%AC%E5%85%AD%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E7%9F%B3%E6%B2%B9%E4%BE%9B%E6%87%89%E9%81%8E%E5%89%A9%E9%87%8F%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC-163053255.html",
