        {
            "title": "舊金山聯儲行長Daly：央行就資產負債表操作進行對外溝通至關重要",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 舊金山聯邦儲備銀行行長Mary Daly表示，中央銀行應致力於向公眾提供關於<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:資產負債表;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/資產負債表\">資產負債表</a>操作的詳細信息，明確其多重職能。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Daly周四在出席都柏林的一次會議前準備好的發言稿顯示，溝通「至關重要」，中央銀行應承認並闡述目標。她補充道，資產負債表操作具有多重功能：在緊急時期提供流動性和金融穩定、在經濟嚴重下行期間刺激經濟，也可只是單純地充當一項有效管理利率的工具。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在許多情況下，這些目標相互交織，同時發生，彼此界限模糊，」她表示。「歸根結底，我們必須投身公眾討論。向外界提供他們需要了解的信息，揭示做出決策的過程，並在經驗或經濟形勢要求時願意進行調整。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-644fa279-8887-3161-90f9-1bfed7fd5cf5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">金融危機與疫情期間，聯儲會官員購入了數萬億美元的資產。此舉導致聯儲會資產負債表大幅擴張，招致外界對部分購買操作的批評，也引起了更廣泛的關於相關操作使聯儲會在金融市場中成為更大存在的批評。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Daly Says Communication Is ‘Essential’ for Balance Sheet</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%88%8A%E9%87%91%E5%B1%B1%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7daly-%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%B1%E8%B3%87%E7%94%A2%E8%B2%A0%E5%82%B5%E8%A1%A8%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C%E9%80%B2%E8%A1%8C%E5%B0%8D%E5%A4%96%E6%BA%9D%E9%80%9A%E8%87%B3%E9%97%9C%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81-135947781.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-13 22:40:57",
