        {
            "title": "習近平將不出席G-20南非峰會 中美俄元首將集體缺席",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"習近平將不出席G-20南非峰會 中美俄元首將集體缺席\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"689\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/vi_1K17jtX3VGvocQYNJUA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4OTtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/b4f4f700-c08d-11f0-b6ff-b208ac26b245\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">習近平將不出席G-20南非峰會 中美俄元首將集體缺席</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
