            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "騰訊與蘋果據悉達成協議 將由蘋果處理微信小遊戲支付並抽取15%佣金",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 據知情人士透露，騰訊控股已與蘋果公司達成一項協議，將由蘋果負責處理微信小遊戲和小程序的支付，並從中抽取15%的佣金。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">兩家科技巨頭之間持續一年多的談判就此塵埃落定，將為蘋果開闢新的收入來源，同時緩解騰訊的壓力。此前蘋果要求騰訊堵住應用開發者所利用的漏洞，開發者通過引導用戶使用外部支付系統來規避蘋果通常收取的30%佣金。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，合格開發者需接受蘋果特定的軟件要求，例如協助家長設置兒童年齡段的要求。因未獲授權公開發言，知情人士要求匿名。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c314c7fe-314f-3639-9235-d0d2d4b3f6ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">騰訊的一位發言人不予置評，蘋果公司的代表未立即回應置評請求。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Apple and Tencent Agree to 15% Fee on WeChat Mini Game Purchases</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Zheping Huang、Debby Wu.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E8%88%87%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E9%81%94%E6%88%90%E5%8D%94%E8%AD%B0-%E5%B0%87%E7%94%B1%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E5%B0%8F%E9%81%8A%E6%88%B2%E6%94%AF%E4%BB%98%E4%B8%A6%E6%8A%BD%E5%8F%9615-%E4%BD%A3%E9%87%91-115922876.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-11-13 20:45:54",
