        },
        {
            "title": "中國10月信貸表現令人失望 政府債券發行疲軟且貸款需求依然低迷",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 中國10月信貸擴張較去年同期放緩的程度超出預期，主要受政府債券發行疲軟及整體借貸需求低迷的拖累。</p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">彭博根據中國人民銀行周四公佈的數據計算顯示，10月廣義信貸衡量指標 —— 社會融資規模 —— 成長8150億元人民幣（1150億美元）。接受彭博調查的經濟學家的預測中值為1.2萬億元，去年同期的增幅為1.4萬億元</p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當月金融機構新增貸款2190億元，而預測中值為4990億元</p></li></ul><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">近期政府債券發行較去年同期放緩，因債券發行計畫提前到了2025年早些時候。另一個因素是季節性因素，每個季度初銀行通常不急於完成貸款目標。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-cd49a11e-55a6-34e6-8e3c-144a34ab4759-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">花旗集團表示，中國5000億元新的政策性融資工具提供的資金可能正在抵消政府債券發行放緩的影響。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由於消費者和企業信心未見明顯復甦跡象，借貸需求也可能依然疲軟。據彭博報導，為完成政府設定的目標，苦於尋找借款人的銀行正越來越多地虛增貸款。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">中國央行已表示對信貸增速的持續放緩保持耐心，稱金融總量增速下降是自然的，與經濟從高速成長轉向高質量發展一致。此番表態降低了市場對年內進一步降息的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題China’s Credit Growth Disappoints With Dip in Public Bond Sales</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B10%E6%9C%88%E4%BF%A1%E8%B2%B8%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E4%BB%A4%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%B1%E6%9C%9B-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E5%82%B5%E5%88%B8%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E7%96%B2%E8%BB%9F%E4%B8%94%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E4%BD%8E%E8%BF%B7-093747679.html",
